    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready to impress! This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and has plenty of life left to give. It drives smoothly and reliably, making it a fantastic choice for daily commutes, road trips, or anything in between. You'll notice some normal signs of use consistent with its age, but nothing that takes away from its solid performance and overall appeal. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be pleasantly surprised!",
